sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant R as Redpanda
    participant C as Consumer
    participant S as Supabase
    participant D as Dashboard

    P->>R: publish event JSON
    R->>C: poll batch
    C->>C: validate Pydantic schema
    alt valide
        C->>S: insert raw_sensor_events
        C->>S: upsert stg + fact
        C->>S: check seuils zone
        opt hors norme
            C->>S: insert fact_quality_alerts
        end
        C->>S: update pipeline_runs
        S-->>D: Realtime refresh
    else invalide
        C->>S: insert dead_letter_events
        C->>S: log data_quality_results fail
    end
